#CHIP K053260
#CLOCK 8000000

; Konami PCM (K053260/K054539) Pitch Tracking Test
;
; Both K053260 and K054539 support pitch modulation of PCM samples.
; This test validates pitch tracking accuracy.
; Can be used for both chips by changing the #CHIP directive.
;
; Tests:
; - Pitch bend over sample range
; - Frequency modulation accuracy
; - Pitch register write timing

#TRACK 0

TEMPO 120

; Start with normal pitch
c4 .

; Pitch up (higher frequency)
d4 .

; Pitch down (lower frequency)
c4 .

r4

; Pitch sweep: ascending
c4 . d4 . e4 . f4 .

r4

; Pitch sweep: descending
g4 . f4 . e4 . d4 .

r4

; Rapid pitch modulation
c4 . . d4 . . e4 . . f4 . .

r2

#END
